course.title: CSS
course.keywords: Discover your internal web designer with our comprehensive CSS course on Gammal Tech. Prerequisite: Completion of the HTML course. Learn how to style and layout web pages, creating visually stunning and responsive designs with CSS. This course is designed to equip you with the knowledge and confidence to enhance your web development skills and build professional websites. Don’t miss the opportunity to elevate your career and turn your web design aspirations into reality. Enroll now and start your journey to becoming a skilled web designer!

subscriptions.title: Monthly Subscription
subscriptions.description: Access to all Gammal Tech courses for one month.

subscriptions.title: Yearly Subscription
subscriptions.description: Access all Gammal Tech courses for one year.
